import React from 'react'
import KatchImage from '../Assets/katch-card.png'
import CaseStudyCard from '../Components/CaseStudyCard'

export default function Katch() {
  return (

    <section className="section-container" id="work">

    <CaseStudyCard
      type = "Primary"
      projectName = "Katch"
      projectDescription = "Flexible meetings with real time availability"
      projectScope = "UI/UX Designer at Katch"
      projectPlatforms = "iOS, Slack"
      projectTimeline = "October '22 - Nov '22"
      projectImage={KatchImage}
    />

    </section>

  )
}
